org.apache.geode.experimental.driver

Class ProtobufRegion<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.geode.experimental.driver.ProtobufRegion<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Type of region keys.
    V - Type of region values.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Region<K,V>

    @Experimental
public class ProtobufRegion<K,V>
extends Object
implements Region<K,V>
    Implements the behaviors of a GemFire region. Send and receives Protobuf messages on the provided socket to communicate with a GemFire server that has Protobuf enabled. This code is an experimental prototype and is presented "as is" with no warranty, suitability, or fitness of purpose implied.
